text: Charles Garnier may refer to: *Charles Garnier (missionary) (1606–1649), Jesuit missionary, martyred in Canada in 1649 *Charles Garnier (architect) (1825–1898), French architect *Charles Garnier (rower) (1887-1963), French Olympic rower ==See also== *Charlie Garner (born 1972), American football player
